# Normalize text files to LF in the working tree on every platform.
#
# Several tests assert absolute byte offsets in parser error output (e.g.
# the yaml_syntax_error fixture). Under Windows' default CRLF checkout each
# preceding line added one byte, shifting those offsets and breaking the
# tests. Forcing LF keeps byte offsets deterministic across platforms.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets must never be line-ending normalized.
*.gz binary
*.zip binary
*.png binary
*.ico binary
